affiliation.name: County of San Diego Communications Office

articleContent: Hundreds of JYNNEOS vaccines are now available at multiple County vaccination events for anyone at risk of getting sick from Mpox. More than 13,000 Mpox vaccines have already been administered and are recommended for anyone in close contact with a confirmed or probable case of MPOX, and gay, bisexual, and other men who have sex with men with multiple partners. The injection is quick, easy and with pop-up locations like the Golden Hill Community Clubhouse in Balboa Park, it is also convenient.
